This Easter, spring themed card is the perfect choice! Featuring a whimsical watercolor painting of a quaint, old town bundt cake shop, this vintage inspired art card is sure to make its recipient smile. The Holey Bundt cake store, designed with the Easter holiday in mind, showcases a festively decorated cakery with window displays full of bundt cakes, cute bunnies, peeps decorations, and a carrot cake special! This seasonal storefront may be closed for now, but the two baby rabbits nibbling on blooming daffodils make for a quiet and charming scene. Not only is this a truly unique card for Easter, but it also doubles as frameable artwork, having been created as the April page of my calendar project. Be sure to check out all the other monthly seasonal storefronts in my shop, and grab yourself a matching set for the year! Price:$3.53
